vote.title: A resolution amending Section 6.1(c)(1) of the City Council Rules of Procedure to state that the City Council voting agenda meetings begin at 9:00 a.m. on the second and fourth Wednesday of each month, with public hearings being conducted no earlier than 1:00 p.m. - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
